title: TU132:  Crisis Exhaustion – Hang in There, it’s Going to Be OK (Eventually) If We Stick Together
description: Together we can protect our hearts from freezing in bitterness, drowning in sorrow, lashing out in justified rage or worse, disconnecting.  Fight the exhaustion that comes with the relentless crises surrounding us now.
itunes:subtitle: Together we can protect our hearts from freezing in bitterness, drowning in sorrow, lashing out in justified rage or worse, disconnecting.
itunes:summary:
Dr. Ann Kelley & Sue Marriott LCSW, CGP reach out to you directly during this time of crisis exhaustion
and total burnout.  Love & connection cannot be stopped by fire, storm, guns or people in temporary power.
Be a weapon of peace.
itunes:author: Ann Kelley, PhD & Sue Marriott LCSW, CGP
itunes:title: Crisis Exhaustion - Hang in There, it's Eventually Going to Be OK...with Sue Marriott and Ann Kelley
